caption.title: Time series of dog rabies cases, dog-bite injuries, and hydrophobia in Osaka Prefecture.
caption.p: The numbers of dog bite injuries were not recorded in 1913, between 1918 and 1921, and between 1929 and 1933. There were no recorded human rabies deaths in 1913, between 1916 and 1919, between 1921 and 1922, and after 1928.
